98
00:08:16,930 --> 00:08:20,188
We can just treat it.

99
00:08:21,650 --> 00:08:23,598
Don't worry, okay?

100
00:08:41,610 --> 00:08:44,228
Hey, you.

101
00:08:45,520 --> 00:08:48,098
It's okay.

102
00:08:57,910 --> 00:09:00,008
Geez.

103
00:09:02,850 --> 00:09:04,048
