Hey, it doesn't hurt. Don't worry.

106
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:19,650
Okay.

107
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:21,998
Don't worry.

108
00:09:21,998 --> 00:09:23,158
<i>Mom...</i>

109
00:09:23,158 --> 00:09:24,768
It's okay.

110
00:09:24,768 --> 00:09:26,758
