207
00:17:25,838 --> 00:17:28,468
- A resting period?
- Yeah.

208
00:17:28,468 --> 00:17:30,218
What do you...

209
00:17:30,218 --> 00:17:32,398
Just like taking a leave from school,

210
00:17:32,398 --> 00:17:35,720
we'd just be taking a break from dating. Not ending it.

211
00:17:37,148 --> 00:17:42,080
I think... that sounds a bit weird.

212
00:17:45,648 --> 00:17:47,958
You never know.

213
00:17:48,848 --> 00:17:51,960
