257
00:21:29,768 --> 00:21:33,318
You worked so hard to get into this college. Why would you take a leave of absence for this?

258
00:21:33,318 --> 00:21:38,058
Did I say I'm going to quit school? I'm just taking a brief break. Don't worry.

259
00:21:38,058 --> 00:21:42,048
Stop the nonsense and continue going to school. I'll do whatever it takes to earn a living–

260
00:21:42,048 --> 00:21:44,040
Forget it!

261
00:21:44,040 --> 00:21:47,278
You just think about getting better.

262
00:21:47,278 --> 00:21:48,868
I'll take care of things.

263
00:21:48,868 --> 00:21:51,208
